      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this motorcar\u2014from its flawless coachwork to the pristine, untouched interior\u2014reflects an uncompromising standard of maintenance. This is an investment-grade acquisition intended for the discerning driver who seeks a specimen in peerless mechanical and aesthetic state. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this benchmark of excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
