      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve meticulously cared for every inch of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
