    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) in impeccable condition. This chassis features the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six powerplant, delivering linear power through the G96 six-speed manual transaxle. The M96 engine has been meticulously sorted with a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal. Mechanical health is verified by a clean DME report with zero Stage 2 overrevs. The suspension geometry remains precise, featuring refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers that maintain factory-spec rebound and compression. The exterior boasts original paint with consistent micron readings across all panels, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key example for the discerning purist seeking optimal throttle response and chassis feedback.",
